<paragraph id="1069CCAB61FFF0E72C3F4D8BB480A2E2" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
MEXICO. Nuevo 
<normalizedToken id="D4EE3E22A958D79233FE729C66A44FF5" originalValue="León">Leon</normalizedToken>
, Monterrey, 
<emphasis id="45EDCD62C02083265E3184259BA70563" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">C.G. Pringle</emphasis>
2840 (holotype GH00054512, isotype VT).
